{"tid":2135010,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Three, Two, One, Fire!  熱血, 熱血, 熱血!  阿冰都好色","createTime":"2020-08-01T06:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T17:41:22.000Z","uid":199804,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c2aad714d52da151ff45a8f3260a4a57b85066","tid":2135010,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"Three, Two, One, Fire!<br />\n熱血, 熱血, 熱血!<br />\n阿冰都好色<br />\n義士義士要出戰一拼<br />\n要操縱泛民誓要出擊<br />\n越過了星空出國<br />\n要得到英籍<br />\n「小心呀　要咬緊泛民呀」<br />\n<br />\n別鄒眉頭今天BNO充足老定<br />\n但00後遺下了也是迷路太不值<br />\n無聊時報學吓搬磚即興<br />\n就連學科都報錯後<br />\n突然成為英籍<br />\n<br />\nGet out, Get out, Get out!<br />\nThis is an Order!<br />\n就要移民姿態優雅<br />\n要分化敵人四眼都花<br />\n就在這TG Group中按一掣封殺<br />\nAttention! Left Turn! Right Turn! March!<br />\n<br />\n機場人流都不多我都出錯閘<br />\n背叛黃營被讚<br />\n龍門冰室太清淡<br />\n被彈時態度太差乜都喊<br />\n若然是出po太慢<br />\n上頭傳來期限時間"},{"pid":"66730645bc9d08275ae96c25c9f1b3fb12467370","tid":2135010,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"法子=Tamama?"},{"pid":"67606d01a03aa9c5f669b78da34594a1764f79dc","tid":2135010,"uid":199804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"66730645bc9d08275ae96c25c9f1b3fb12467370","tid":2135010,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"法子=Tamama?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"Keroro=皇上 <br />\nTamama=法子<br />\nKururu=四眼<br />\nGiroro=泰博<br />\nDororo=兆健<br />\n摩亞=BoA=四眼"},{"pid":"daaf02477d64e4293bcf4203e04933cf954a0e20","tid":2135010,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac140911d7f1cd4921b898afc5dc57a5cb7e0a80","tid":2135010,"uid":209073,"like":0,"dislike"